dcterms:description: The Diginetica dataset provides transactional data with rich item attribute information, including category, priceLog2, and item name tokens. It is used for session-based recommendations.

dcterms:description: The MX Player dataset is constructed from the MX Player log, containing interaction sequences on movies with rich attribute information. It is used for recommendations in the MX Player application.
